short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quick reference for ASTM material properties used in construction

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With a single click, this tool sheds light on the yield and ultimate strength of various materials. 

For the truly curious, a single click unlocks a hidden wellspring of knowledge.  Delve into the depths of material information, unearthing additional details that may hold the key to your next project.
